together, let them know we're back?

785
00:57:28,905 --> 00:57:31,785
"Dear Josh...

786
00:57:32,425 --> 00:57:33,945
...and Erin."

787
00:57:34,345 --> 00:57:37,225
Oh, sure. You get the easy part.

788
00:57:40,745 --> 00:57:41,785
"We're...

789
00:57:43,145 --> 00:57:44,345
