792
00:57:52,345 --> 00:57:54,824
That's not a sentence.
It's a preposition and a continent.

793
00:57:55,064 --> 00:57:57,464
I crossed out your period
and made a sentence.

794
00:57:57,624 --> 00:58:00,744
See? "We're back from Europe."
Your turn.

795
00:58:00,984 --> 00:58:01,944
Thank you.

796
00:58:02,824 --> 00:58:06,744
Exclamation point.
Comma. Close parentheses.

797
00:58:07,064 --> 00:58:08,984
"But l...

798
00:58:09,704 --> 00:58:11,704
...don't want to talk...

799
00:58:11,944 --> 00:58:14,264
...about grammar."

800
00:58:14,504 --> 00:58:18,904
Colon. "I want to...

801
00:58:19,784 --> 00:58:21,784
...make love to...

802
00:58:22,104 --> 00:58:24,183
...your mother."

803
00:58:25,783 --> 00:58:27,783
No, you didn't write that.

804
00:58:30,823 --> 00:58:33,463
What? I do. I want to.

805
00:58:33,703 --> 00:58:35,463
After we finish the letter.

806
00:58:35,703 --> 00:58:39,783
No, let's make love right now.
Then we write the letter.

807
00:58:40,023 --> 00:58:43,303
Come on, we only had
a couple of sentences to go.

808
00:58:43,623 --> 00:58:46,663
In Europe, you would've
made love first.

809
00:58:47,783 --> 00:58:50,343
-What's that supposed to mean?
-Nothing.

810
00:58:50,583 --> 00:58:53,302
-That I'm not spontaneous?
-I'm not saying that.

811
00:58:53,462 --> 00:58:55,222
But that's what you implied.

812
00:58:55,462 --> 00:58:57,702
That in Europe I'd have
made love, but here--

813
00:58:57,942 --> 00:59:00,022
I don't want us to get to the point...

814
00:59:00,342 --> 00:59:03,702
...where we can't make love unless
there's a concierge downstairs.

815
00:59:03,942 --> 00:59:08,502
I wanted to take three minutes
to finish a letter to our children...

816
00:59:08,662 --> 00:59:10,102
...who I haven't seen--

817
00:59:10,262 --> 00:59:13,942
What's that supposed to mean?
That I don't care about our children?

818
00:59:14,102 --> 00:59:16,342
If I finish the letter,
I could be spontaneous.

819
00:59:16,502 --> 00:59:19,462
That's not spontaneous!
That's making an appointment!

820
00:59:19,702 --> 00:59:22,341
I was in the mood
for unscheduled affection...

821
00:59:22,581 --> 00:59:24,661
