835
01:00:04,260 --> 01:00:06,580
You're damn straight
I'll bring it up again!

836
01:00:06,820 --> 01:00:08,660
I haven't spoken to her
in six months!

837
01:00:08,900 --> 01:00:11,460
Not once have you seen it
through my eyes!

838
01:00:11,700 --> 01:00:14,900
We don't have a pea under our mattress.
You know what we have?

839
01:00:15,140 --> 01:00:16,260
A fucking watermelon!

840
01:00:16,580 --> 01:00:18,740
