841
01:00:18,900 --> 01:00:20,740
Oh, fuck it!

842
01:00:21,140 --> 01:00:22,739
Jesus!

843
01:00:30,419 --> 01:00:32,019
Welcome home.

844
01:00:40,259 --> 01:00:41,539
Bye, Dad.

845
01:00:42,019 --> 01:00:43,859
-Thanks.
-I love you.

846
01:00:44,979 --> 01:00:46,659
-Bye, Mom.
-Buddy.

847
01:00:48,899 --> 01:00:50,259
Love you.

848
01:00:51,219 --> 01:00:52,978
See you guys in a month.

849
