Bye, you guys.

850
01:01:02,098 --> 01:01:03,458
-Bye, Daddy.
-Couple of weeks.

851
01:01:03,618 --> 01:01:05,778
-Watch your toes.
-See you.

852
01:01:05,938 --> 01:01:07,378
Bye, kids.

853
01:01:23,297 --> 01:01:25,697
