859
01:01:53,136 --> 01:01:56,496
You know, since you're a writer,
I know you'd appreciate...

860
01:01:56,736 --> 01:01:59,216
...that the sister
of Bette Davis' chauffeur...

861
01:01:59,456 --> 01:02:02,736
...once had Thanksgiving
in the apartment next door.

862
01:02:03,376 --> 01:02:04,496
Really?

863
01:02:05,536 --> 01:02:07,936
Are there any other kids
in this building?

864
01:02:08,176 --> 01:02:12,176
Oodles! Including, if I might add,
the nephew of the actor...

865
01:02:12,336 --> 01:02:15,696
