the fourth lifeboat on Titanic.

866
01:02:15,936 --> 01:02:18,656
Rent the film, you'll see.
I'll introduce you.

867
01:02:18,896 --> 01:02:22,895
I'm showing it to another family today,
but if you're interested...

868
01:02:23,055 --> 01:02:26,095
...I can hold it for you,
give your wife a look-see--

869
01:02:26,335 --> 01:02:27,135
I'm interested.

870
01:02:27,375 --> 01:02:31,535
Who wouldn't be? Look how the light
from that window fills the room.

871
01:02:32,175 --> 01:02:33,935
