872
01:02:34,095 --> 01:02:36,895
...to the man who did the voice
of Charlie the Tuna...

873
01:02:37,215 --> 01:02:40,895
...he said, and I quote,
"Wow," unquote.

874
01:02:41,135 --> 01:02:42,975
I think that says it all.

875
01:02:45,615 --> 01:02:47,375
First, you put olive oil...

876
01:02:47,615 --> 01:02:49,375
