877
01:02:49,615 --> 01:02:52,094
Sauté until garlic turn light brown.

878
01:02:52,414 --> 01:02:55,854
Make sure that your wok have
a strong heat underneath it.

879
01:02:56,094 --> 01:02:59,054
Now take an egg and crack it
to the hot oil.

880
01:03:01,294 --> 01:03:05,214
Make sure all the ingredients
are cooked thoroughly.

881
01:03:06,574 --> 01:03:07,534
You okay?

882
01:03:07,694 --> 01:03:09,854
Yeah, I'm fine.

883
01:03:10,814 --> 01:03:13,054
Now we add some Pad Thai noodle.

884
01:03:14,974 --> 01:03:18,574
I saw Deirdre up at Parents' Weekend,
but I didn't see you.

885
01:03:18,894 --> 01:03:20,733
I went up the weekend before.

886
01:03:20,973 --> 01:03:22,893
You know, since the divorce...

887
01:03:23,133 --> 01:03:26,813
...it's a lot easier for everyone
if we come up at separate times.

888
01:03:27,213 --> 01:03:30,253
Kevin and I took a great hike
up to that waterfall.

889
01:03:30,413 --> 01:03:32,093
You and Ben take that hike?

890
01:03:32,333 --> 01:03:34,653
Yeah, it was beautiful.

891
01:03:35,293 --> 01:03:37,853
Spice it up with some chili pepper.

892
01:03:38,093 --> 01:03:41,133
You know, spicy food
make a better lover.

893
01:03:41,453 --> 01:03:43,693
