the hotter you get.

894
01:03:45,133 --> 01:03:47,533
Well, the spicier the better for me.

895
01:03:49,133 --> 01:03:50,332
Rice vinegar.

896
01:03:54,492 --> 01:03:55,932
Does Ben like Thai food?

897
01:03:58,492 --> 01:04:00,172
