898
01:04:00,332 --> 01:04:01,772
Ben and I are di--

899
01:04:02,412 --> 01:04:03,612
Separated.

900
01:04:05,132 --> 01:04:06,652
Gee, I had no idea.

901
01:04:06,972 --> 01:04:09,292
