903
01:04:11,772 --> 01:04:14,092
I'm so sorry. How long?

904
01:04:15,132 --> 01:04:19,132
72 hours, four weeks, five years...

905
01:04:19,372 --> 01:04:21,691
...depending on when
you start counting.

906
01:04:21,851 --> 01:04:24,971
I'm really sorry.
I know how hard it can be.

907
01:04:28,171 --> 01:04:29,691
This will sound crazy...

908
01:04:30,011 --> 01:04:33,371
...but I always enjoyed
Erin and Josh's appointments...

909
01:04:33,611 --> 01:04:36,491
...because it gave me a chance
to get to know you.

910
01:04:37,051 --> 01:04:39,851
But when you called me
about your bite...

911
01:04:40,171 --> 01:04:44,651
...I felt myself looking forward to it
because I knew we'd be alone.

912
01:04:45,851 --> 01:04:48,891
And just tell me if it's too soon...

913
01:04:49,770 --> 01:04:53,370
...but I wondered if maybe you
wanted to have dinner sometime?

914
01:04:55,370 --> 01:04:56,970
