915
01:04:58,890 --> 01:05:02,410
I was thinking of something
that didn't involve a teacher.

916
01:05:06,010 --> 01:05:08,010
You always hear people say...

917
01:05:08,170 --> 01:05:10,490
...they stayed too long
in a bad marriage.

918
01:05:10,730 --> 01:05:14,490
For the longest time, I never thought
of my marriage as being bad.

919
01:05:14,730 --> 01:05:18,410
I thought love was something you
were allowed to fall in and out of.

920
01:05:18,570 --> 01:05:20,489
You know, peaks and valleys.

921
01:05:21,129 --> 01:05:22,729
But after a while...

922
01:05:23,049 --> 01:05:26,249
...the peaks get lower
and further apart.

923
01:05:26,409 --> 01:05:30,329
Then one day you find yourself
wondering, "Is this who I really am?

924
01:05:30,569 --> 01:05:33,929
Someone who has taken up permanent
residence in the valley?

925
01:05:34,169 --> 01:05:37,929
Or is this just who I am
with this person?"

926
01:05:39,369 --> 01:05:41,849
