927
01:05:42,089 --> 01:05:45,689
"Maybe there is another version
of my life, of myself...

928
01:05:45,929 --> 01:05:48,169
...that's a happier one. "

929
01:06:05,448 --> 01:06:06,888
Bullshit.

930
01:06:08,568 --> 01:06:11,768
"Yossel looked into Minnie's eyes
and felt...

931
01:06:13,368 --> 01:06:14,648
...nothing.

932
01:06:14,968 --> 01:06:19,207
